{"tid":469394,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每人心中都有一個解唔開既心結...","createTime":"2017-11-15T09:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T13:32:53.000Z","uid":139272,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a5bb9f8f974020cea1b0915b77391393b0349f4c","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"呢個心結，你一直以黎都好想解開佢，<br />\n但以自己一人之力根本就好難解決。<br />\n有D死結，你始終都無辦法解得開，<br />\n有D死結，有人幫你一齊化解左。<br />\n有時候，身邊既人會同你講，<br />\n「其實你果件事都無咩大不了姐! 只係你諗太多啦!」<br />\n但其實所謂既無咩大不了，其實都係因為旁人無親身經歷而無法體會<br />\n有D經歷，話放下，好輕易，做起來，就難上加難。<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個心結，你就一直唔理，拖到而家都未解決......<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49331f1fb9892cc695bf27d1a54926cd8fa903c2","tid":469394,"uid":3908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57d4c7b789fb6d386e875d38ae9bef36f2c0434a","tid":469394,"uid":41737,"like":24,"dislike":9,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7ef0743bb590c974208608c2eb5a4de103a881c","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"唔知大家係咪都有自己既心結呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f45626f7be9712a9453785c8ffa1022a7545a7","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放鬆啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n放鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時我都覺得自己需要"},{"pid":"c65da549538a790e8142b184f20de7a20e66a82d","tid":469394,"uid":74262,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b945701787511d8d6076fa410ce726288730843f","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<img src=\