ets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住開始傷春悲秋，覺得自己陷入苦戀，凄美浪漫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個女仔同男仔傾兩句，就覺得有人比帽佢戴，嬲到震曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快就會忍唔住戇撚尻尻，死就死唔做實後悔，唔照下鏡先，自殺式表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      <br />\n毒撚表白嚇死條女，派好人卡，再Block尻佢，毒撚就開始惱羞成怒發爛渣，怪條女做乜比錯覺佢，賤格收佢做兵，冇興趣做乜要同我傾計同我text，之後再上高登屌條女係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n憤怒過後，自我陶醉自覺經歷失戀，再次傷春悲秋，認定自己受到情傷，曾經滄海難為水，除卻巫山不是雲，再自命看透世事，「自我選擇」拒絕動情，一個人自在更開心，全部女人都係雞！溝女既係狗公MK！拍拖既直刻死！撞車死！生Cancer！換唔到心死！抵撚死！哈哈哈！全部係雞！全部都蝦尻毒撚！全部仆街死！哈哈..哈！！<br />\n<br />\n毒撚，Are you ready?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁似講緊我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada8cc9d7731b7e94769a9c4095c968331caf81a","tid":469394,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"心結：升中四了"},{"pid":"d16b6ed1e5bd66d90fb5df3c95f50191633cd86c","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備星期六去見社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞咩要見社工啊!?"},{"pid":"c65131c6e9b46bcb8536be86d4feafba01c43e7b","tid":469394,"uid":139272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前女友出軌加床照呢個真係心結<br />\n<br />\n我估呢世都唔會解得開最多係淡忘</blo